Key Match Events: India run through the rest of the order
Craig Ervine chips Hardik Pandya back to the bowler
Tony Munyonga gets hit by a Shami yorker
Sikandar Raza and Ryan Burl build a 50-run partnership
Burl has been in especially searing boundary-hitting form
Ashwin tosses one right up, and foxes Burl
Madhevere follows it and Virat Kohli takes an excellent diving catch at short cover
Arshdeep Singh swings one back through Regis Chakabva's bat and pad and hits timber
Craig Ervine gets a couple of fours away
Sean Williams hits Mohammad Shami for six
A thick outside edge off Williams carries to Bhuvneshwar Kumar. Shami has a wicket
Zimbabwe are in a dire position, at 29 for 3
Miscellaneous Highlights: The game may be one-sided, as Zimbabwe lose their eighth. But more than 82,000 people have turned up to watch this game. Incredible.
